title: Paul McCartney Live Halifax N.S. July 11 2009 High Def
description:
Halifax Commons was the first concert of that summer tour, Paul was naturally pumped up for the show. Nova Scotia which stands for New Scotland, was an excellent venue to perform Mull Of Kintyre.
